Man.

00:48.840 --> 00:50.383
Oh, man.

00:52.594 --> 00:54.095
Damn it.

00:54.137 --> 00:56.222
You never get a second chance
to make a first impression.

00:56.264 --> 00:59.184
You know?
[engine starting]

00:59.225 --> 01:01.561
Hey!
Oh, no, no, no, no! No!

01:05.231 --> 01:06.524
This time it's loaded.

01:06.566 --> 01:08.068
Six bullets,
each with your name on it

01:08.109 --> 01:10.111
if you don't get out
of my car right now!

01:12.614 --> 01:14.616
