I'm willing to negotiate.

01:14.657 --> 01:16.159
[engine sputtering]

01:16.201 --> 01:20.038
Oh, I guess Evelyn
doesn't like you very much.

01:20.080 --> 01:21.498
I'll make you a deal.

01:21.539 --> 01:23.750
You scooch over,
I'll get you out of this alive.

01:23.792 --> 01:24.793
But you better
think fast,

01:24.834 --> 01:27.128
'cause that ain't
no birthday clown.

01:31.675 --> 01:33.510
Okay, go!

01:35.637 --> 01:36.971
[horn honks]

01:37.013 --> 01:40.183
Oh, shit.

01:41.976 --> 01:46.064
Okay, L1, R1, up, down, left,
right, right, down, up.

01:46.106 --> 01:50.485
[engine revving]

01:50.527 --> 01:51.945
All right, Evelyn,
we have nine days

01:51.986 --> 01:53.238
