09:23.772 --> 09:25.607
- Sounds like
you have trust issues.

09:25.648 --> 09:26.941
- Yeah,
you're not wrong.

09:26.983 --> 09:28.651
Nice pipes, dude,
I have to say.

09:28.693 --> 09:31.112
That high note, whoo!
