09:31.154 --> 09:33.448
- Oh, word?
- Yeah, can I go?

09:33.490 --> 09:34.783
I got somewhere to be.

09:34.824 --> 09:36.409
- I thought you said
you were coming to the show!

09:36.451 --> 09:39.496
- Of course, I am.

09:39.537 --> 09:42.415
