after the show?

09:46.211 --> 09:50.590
- Well, in that case,
tonight is opening night!

09:50.632 --> 09:52.801
[laughing]

09:54.636 --> 09:56.179
- How were your showers?

09:56.221 --> 09:57.889
- Aw, I don't know
the last time

09:57.931 --> 10:00.392
