Uh, sir.

10:01.685 --> 10:03.186
- Consider it
your recompense

10:03.228 --> 10:05.313
for upholding
law and order.

10:05.355 --> 10:11.069
Warm showers, warm blankets,
warm meals.

10:11.111 --> 10:14.197
- Oh.
- Aw, fuck, mashed potatoes?

10:14.239 --> 10:17.117
- [Mike] And goddamn,
look at all that gravy!

10:17.158 --> 10:19.911
I wonder how we can get
one of those punch cards.

10:19.953 --> 10:23.415
- Now, let's proceed
to your initiation.

10:27.168 --> 10:28.545
Right this way,
gentlemen.

10:30.839 --> 10:33.967
What you see down there
is our supply truck.

10:34.009 --> 10:35.802
It brings us
important provisions.

10:35.844 --> 10:38.972
As you can see,
it's broken down.

10:39.014 --> 10:40.890
That's why
it's not moving.

10:40.932 --> 10:45.186
What I need for you to do
is to protect that truck.

10:45.228 --> 10:46.604
- From what?

10:46.646 --> 10:48.481
