Listen, I really appreciate
you coming along willingly.

11:03.955 --> 11:05.665
Normally I have to drag people
into the theater

11:05.707 --> 11:06.958
kicking and screaming.

11:07.000 --> 11:08.752
But word of advice,

11:08.793 --> 11:11.212
you won't like
what happens if you run.

11:13.548 --> 11:14.674
What? Oh, him?

11:14.716 --> 11:15.925
Nah, he was here
before.

11:15.967 --> 11:17.052
Hey, Donald.

11:17.093 --> 11:19.012
