on our supplies,

13:13.001 --> 13:15.503
it's open season.

13:15.545 --> 13:16.921
- What the hell?

13:16.963 --> 13:18.965
Hey, why do you
call 'em seagulls?

13:19.007 --> 13:20.675
These look like
normal survivors to me.

13:20.717 --> 13:23.636
- What else would you call
a bunch of fucking trash eaters?

13:33.605 --> 13:36.232
- Dude, are we really
gonna kill these guys?

