- I saved your ass.

14:11.226 --> 14:13.853
- [Agent Stone] Seagulls,
butchers, exiles.

14:13.895 --> 14:17.190
They see the world
in shades of gray.

14:17.232 --> 14:19.859
What I need
from you two lawmen

14:19.901 --> 14:21.069
is to just show them

14:21.111 --> 14:23.697
that there's only two colors
in the world,

14:23.738 --> 14:27.283
black and blue.

14:27.325 --> 14:31.246
Now, you missed, Stu.
It can happen to anyone.

14:31.287 --> 14:33.790
Rookie mistake.

14:33.832 --> 14:36.835
Hey, don't let it
happen again.

14:39.587 --> 14:41.464
Okay.

14:41.506 --> 14:44.342
You guys want
some burgers?

14:44.384 --> 14:46.428
- Bubby-baby,
bubby-baby.

14:46.469 --> 14:48.138
