up the ass.

15:03.486 --> 15:05.947
No, I sleep here
because it reminds me

15:05.989 --> 15:08.366
of where I was
before Vegas.

15:08.408 --> 15:11.327
Back then, I lived with
a real solid group of dudes.

15:11.369 --> 15:14.998
But then the world took a shit
and I came to Sin City.

15:15.040 --> 15:18.460
Now that was a party.

15:18.501 --> 15:21.087
- You've been here alone
for over two decades?

15:21.129 --> 15:24.007
- Oh, shit, has it been
that long?

15:24.049 --> 15:25.258
Look at this guy.

15:25.300 --> 15:27.886
Hasn't aged a day.
What a beauty.

15:27.927 --> 15:29.262
Nah, I'm not alone.

15:29.304 --> 15:31.264
I got Harold,
which, have you--

15:31.306 --> 15:32.932
you haven't met
Harold yet.

15:32.974 --> 15:35.769
I'm gonna introduce you.

15:35.810 --> 15:38.396
This is Harold.

15:38.438 --> 15:40.607
Been my best friend
since I was a kid.

15:40.648 --> 15:42.901
You know, my entire life
people have been lying to me.

15:42.942 --> 15:45.362
Even my fucking parents!

15:45.403 --> 15:47.405
But, uh, never Harold.

15:47.447 --> 15:50.950
