He can't lie to anyone.

15:50.992 --> 15:52.535
- I can see that.

15:52.577 --> 15:53.661
[sighing]

15:53.703 --> 15:55.622
- I don't know what I'd do
without him.

15:55.663 --> 15:57.665
Look at that smile.

15:57.707 --> 15:59.376
So, you got a Harold?

15:59.417 --> 16:01.628
- No.
I got an Evelyn.

16:01.670 --> 16:03.296
- Oh, that's cute.

16:03.338 --> 16:07.467
- Before I met her,
being alone was all I knew.

16:07.509 --> 16:09.969
You know, she makes
everything easier, you know?

16:10.011 --> 16:13.640
Sometimes I wish I could
make her laugh. Right?

16:13.682 --> 16:15.308
I have to say
after all this time

16:15.350 --> 16:17.894
